data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!!  A must see!!!   This property has so much to offer. A beautiful remodeled farmhouse style home nestled on 1.463 MOL acres of land. The main home is 5 bedrooms with 4 bathrooms. 3 of those bedrooms are master suites with bathrooms attached.  All updated and move in ready.  Main house has a beautifully updated kitchen and updated floors through out the house. The exterior has a a three bay shop on one side and an additional two bay shop on the other side. There is also additional covered parking for car or boat. It also has an attached but separate living area that has living room, kitchen, bedroom, bathroom and upstairs room that can also be an office. This additional living space has its own driveway and separate entrance. Could possibly be rented out to generate additional income. owner is including 2 refrigerators and the zero turn mower.
